parameters:
Outnumbered or not, to be caught off guard by such people...
I still have much to learn.

I want to avoid standing out right now, yet to suffer such
humiliation...! And to wrinkle the borrowed costume so much.
Just when I was starting to like it!

More importantly, I wonder if the girl who was being
harassed is safe. I must hurry back and help her...!!

Even so... hmm... no matter how much I wipe, the line won't
come off... Is this okay?
